description:
The last time I saw Kipper he said he was "sorting things out" regarding his sexuality.
He told me then that he'd "probably" be back for more and I didn't doubt it.
He was pretty nervous around Joe at first, but Joe exudes a sort of sexual hunger that really gets things going.
I was really impressed at our little Kipper's first time. He gave Joe quite the fucking!
title: Kipper & Joe
